About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. snippet.title: Avengers: Doomsday - First Trailer (2026) Marvel Studios
snippet.description:
‚Äî Attention Viewers ‚ö†Ô∏è
‚Äî This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
‚Äî Avengers: Doomsday

‚Äî Music Credits - https://youtu.be/6Ot-gRruxng

‚Äî This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I‚Äôve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support ‚Äî now let‚Äôs dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. üé¨‚ú®

‚Äî In this concept trailer for Avengers: Doomsday, the story centers on the long-unresolved consequences of Steve Rogers‚Äô final choice in Endgame, revealing that his decision to remain in the past fractured reality in ways the Avengers never anticipated. As timelines splinter and the stability of the main MCU begins to erode, Steve is forced back into the conflict, confronting the personal cost of his legacy and the ripple effects of his sacrifice. The narrative hints at a corrupted alternate reality where familiar heroes took darker paths, drawing Doctor Doom into the heart of the multiversal crisis and threatening total collapse across worlds. With time itself no longer trustworthy, Rogers emerges as both the cause and the possible solution, facing a reckoning that could determine whether the prime timeline survives or is rewritten forever.

snippet.title: Arjun Katuwal - Teri Meri Kahani (Official Music Video) Nimesh Shrestha || Barsha kshetri || Vague
snippet.description:
This song is a humble tribute to the beautiful but heartbreaking love story of Bibek Pangeni and Srijana Subedi, a couple who showed the world what true love, courage, and devotion really look like.
Their journey reminded us that love is not just about the smiles we share, but also the battles we fight together, hand in hand.
It is our way of honoring a love that touched millions and continues to inspire people everywhere.

To Bibek, your strength and smile will never be forgotten.
To Srijana, your love and dedication remain a timeless example of what it means to stand by someone with your whole heart.
And to everyone watching, may their story remind you to cherish the people you love a little more today.

snippet.title: Supergirl | Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Look out. #Supergirl lands in theaters June 26.

‚ÄúSupergirl,‚Äù DC Studios‚Äô newest feature film to hit the big screen, will be in theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures, starring Milly Alcock in the dual role of Supergirl/Kara Zor-El.  Craig Gillespie directs the film from a screenplay by Ana Nogueira.

When an unexpected and ruthless adversary strikes too close to home, Kara Zor-El, aka Supergirl, reluctantly joins forces with an unlikely companion on an epic, interstellar journey of vengeance and justice.

Alcock stars alongside Matthias Schoenaerts, Eve Ridley, David Krumholtz, Emily Beecham, and Jason Momoa.

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and James Gunn are producing the film, which is based on characters from DC, Supergirl based on characters created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.  The film is executive produced by Nigel Gostelow, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars P. Winther.  Behind the camera, Gillespie is joined by director of photography Rob Hardy, production designer Neil Lamont, editor Tatiana S. Riegel, costume designer Anna B. Sheppard, Visual Effects Supervisor Geoffrey Baumann, and composer Ramin Djawadi.  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment Production, The Safran Company Production, A Film by Craig Gillespie, ‚ÄúSupergirl,‚Äù which will be in theaters and IMAX¬Æ across North America on June 26, 2026, and internationally beginning 24 June 2026, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

Alcock stars alongside Matthias Schoenaerts, Eve Ridley, David Krumholtz, Emily Beecham, and Jason Momoa.

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and James Gunn are producing the film, which is based on characters from DC, Supergirl based on characters created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.  The film is executive produced by Nigel Gostelow, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars P. Winther.  Behind the camera, Gillespie is joined by director of photography Rob Hardy, production designer Neil Lamont, editor Tatiana S. Riegel, costume designer Anna B. Sheppard, Visual Effects Supervisor Geoffrey Baumann, and composer Ramin Djawadi.  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment Production, The Safran Company Production, A Film by Craig Gillespie, ‚ÄúSupergirl,‚Äù which will be in theaters and IMAX¬Æ across North America on June 26, 2026, and internationally beginning 24 June 2026, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: Anuv Jain - INAAM (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
The 15th studio recorded single - Inaam, written, sung and composed by #AnuvJain is here!

Listen to 'Inaam' on all streaming platforms : https://UMGI.lnk.to/Inaam_AnuvJain


Audio Credits: 

Artist: Anuv Jain (@anuvjain)
Composer: Anuv Jain (@anuvjain)
Producer: Lost Stories (@loststories)
Guitars: Keba Jeremiah (@kebajr)
Choirs: Solomon Konwar (@eskay______) Prachi Kapil (@prachi.kapil8)
Mix Engineers: Rishab Joshi (@rishabjoshi) & Mukul Jain (@mixbymukul)
Master Engineer: Mukul Jain (@mixbymukul)
Recording Engineer: Jay Rana (@itsjayrana)
Additional Programming: Sarthak Kalyani (@sarthak.kalyani)
Dolby Atmos Mastered at Ferris Wheel Studios (@ferriswheelstudios)

Video Credits: 

Director: Bhagyesh Rajeshirke (@bhagyesh_rajeshirke)
Associate Director: Manthan Sharma (@manthan.mp4)
Creative Director: Pranjal Asha (@pranjalasha)
Editor: Manthan Sharma (@manthan.mp4)
Producer: Arnab Kar (@arnab_kar)

Management: REPRESENT
Managers: Shirsodhi Banerjee (@shirsodhi), Kartik Iyer (@kartik_iyer_)

Inaam Lyrics: 

Paragraph 1

Malum 
Hai na 
Hum janay 
Tumko tumse zyada

Tumko 
Mila hai woh
Saalon se 
Jo bhi hai manga

Pre-chorus 1

Kaise khilono ki 
Ro ro ke
Karte the mangay 

Ik bar mil jaye 
Do din mein
Hi bhul jatay  

Chorus 1

Lekin khilono ke dil 
Toh hote hi nahin the

Dil toh humara hai 
Janay galat kya sahi yeh

Kitna the chahte par
Ab tumko yaad na aatey 
Hum

Paragraph 2

Kya yaad tumko 
Tum humko
‚ÄòInaam‚Äô the kehte 

Karte the kitna kuch
Panay ki chah 
Mein pehlay 


Pre-chorus 2

Ab yeh inaam ka 
Tum pe ilzaam hai jana

Dil hai gawah
Jeete jabse ho
Tumko hai hara 

Chorus 2

Cheezein badalti hain 
Itna toh hum ne bhi mana

Itna badal jaogay 
Jana kisne tha jana  

Jo tha parvana 
Ab usko humari parwah na 
Kyun?

Pre-Bridge

Dil mein baat kya hai?
Haan bolo humse 

Chahta aur kya hai? 
Haan bolo humse

Kya kami yahan hai?
Haan bolo humse na

Jo kaha mila hai
Haan bolo humse 

Badle mein bhala hai
Haan bolo humse

Manga tumse kya hai
Hai manga zara sa hi, kya hi, 

Kya? haye

Bas 

Bridge

Jo khat likhe the tumne 
Unhe padh bhi lo zara 
Waadein kiye the jo bhi
Nibhao na aise kabhi

In waadon ki siyahi 
Abhi sukhi hi kahan?
Hai tumhari hi likhai
Yaan bhule ho ye bhi?

Paragraph 3

Kehne ko 
Wah wah 
Tum phir se 
Inaam ho jeete 

Chehre par
Muskan 
Par ankhein hain
Khush na kahin se 

Pre-chorus 3

Humne kaha tha
Hum janey tumko 
Tumse zyada 

Shayad galat the 
Par itna toh 
Humne hai jana 

Chorus 3

Har woh inaam 
Qadar ke bina hi hai waise 

Ghar mein padhe, 
Dhul khate khilono ke jaise

Pal bhar behlaye 
Par dil ko yeh khush na kar paye 
Yoon

Hidden verse

Ghar bethe likhta tha 
Dil ki kahani meri 

Charon taraf thi deewarein 
Deewaron se hi 

Kehta tha ik din 
Jahaan hoga haathon mein hi

Aa aa

Jo tha gumnamo mein 
Ab woh inaamon pe bhi 

Qaidi hai, Qaid hi hai 
Phir bhi dewaron mein hi 

Namumkin khwabon mein
Na khush udane meri 

Aa aa

Ab yeh inaam ka 
Tum pe ilzaam hai jana

Dil hai gawah
Jeete jabse ho
Tumko hai hara 

Chorus 2

Cheezein badalti hain 
Itna toh hum ne bhi mana

Itna badal jaogay 
Jana kisne tha jana  

Jo tha parvana 
Ab usko humari parwah na 
Kyun?

Pre-Bridge

Dil mein baat kya hai?
Haan bolo humse 

Chahta aur kya hai? 
Haan bolo humse

Kya kami yahan hai?
Haan bolo humse na

Jo kaha mila hai
Haan bolo humse 

Badle mein bhala hai
Haan bolo humse

Manga tumse kya hai
Hai manga zara sa hi, kya hi, 

Kya? haye

Bas 

Bridge

Jo khat likhe the tumne 
Unhe padh bhi lo zara 
Waadein kiye the jo bhi
Nibhao na aise kabhi

In waadon ki siyahi 
Abhi sukhi hi kahan?
Hai tumhari hi likhai
Yaan bhule ho ye bhi?

Paragraph 3

Kehne ko 
Wah wah 
Tum phir se 
Inaam ho jeete 

Chehre par
Muskan 
Par ankhein hain
Khush na kahin se 

Pre-chorus 3

Humne kaha tha
Hum janey tumko 
Tumse zyada 

Shayad galat the 
Par itna toh 
Humne hai jana 

Chorus 3

Har woh inaam 
Qadar ke bina hi hai waise 

Ghar mein padhe, 
Dhul khate khilono ke jaise

Pal bhar behlaye 
Par dil ko yeh khush na kar paye 
Yoon

Hidden verse

Ghar bethe likhta tha 
Dil ki kahani meri 

Charon taraf thi deewarein 
Deewaron se hi 

Kehta tha ik din 
Jahaan hoga haathon mein hi

Aa aa

Jo tha gumnamo mein 
Ab woh inaamon pe bhi 

Qaidi hai, Qaid hi hai 
Phir bhi dewaron mein hi 

Namumkin khwabon mein
Na khush udane meri 

Aa aa

snippet.title: Shaky ( Official #Video ) Sanju Rathod Ft. Isha Malviya | G-Spark | New #Marathi Songs 2025
snippet.description:
Provided To Youtube By Amal Star Media
| üïâ ||
Sanju Rathod presents 'Shaky' a Marathi track like no other!

Shaky is a fresh Marathi Pop anthem that blends playful Afrobeat grooves with everyday desi charm. Sanju Rathod and Isha Malviya bring effortless swag, catchy hooks, and vibrant energy in this fun, feel-good love track. A bold, danceable vibe that pushes Marathi music into exciting new territory.

A brand-new fusion of Selo and Nadhing Selo arrives with the energetic creation ‚ÄúAankhama Chasma Chyattai.‚Äù This special version carries emotion, rhythm, and nostalgia as Roj Moktan and Jamuna Yonjan lend their voices together after 20 long years, creating a powerful moment of musical reunion.

The lyrics, written by Jivan Bomjan Tamang and Roj Moktan, pair seamlessly with the music composed by Roj Moktan, giving the song a modern heartbeat while preserving its cultural depth.

The music video features dynamic performances by Amir Dong, Bipashna Tamang, Nisha Lama, and Kuisang Rumba, each adding expressive storytelling that enhances the flow and feeling of the song.

Guided by the direction of Amir Dong, the visuals carry a strong sense of culture, emotion, and cinematic style, resulting in a compelling and memorable presentation.

This music video is exclusively available on Roj Moktan‚Äôs Official YouTube Channel, with no reuploads or distribution permitted on any other platforms.

snippet.description:
You asked for it. The path to 6 hunters begins. I need to prove that I have the skills and work my way up the Minecraft Manhunt ladder.

Follow my socials:
‚ûΩ Twitter - @dream
‚ûΩ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
‚ûΩ Snapchat - @dream

George: @GeorgeNotFound   

We decided to call this series Minecraft Manhunt. This video is a different rendition of it, where there is ONE hunter, but I am NOT allowed to wear any armor. Not a single piece. 

This is a new Minecraft but, 1.21.10 challenge that we have decided to try. I try to beat the game, while my friend George tries to prevent me from doing it. It's a race, and it's super intense and we had a lot of laughs. I love doing these challenges.

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin

Music is from: @dreamproductionsXD 

#MinecraftManhunt

snippet.title: Timi Merai [Timro Lagi]- Neetesh Jung Kunwar (Official Audio W Lyrics)
snippet.description:
This time, I dedicate this song to the one who picks me up every single time I fall. I may not be good with my words but that won't change my love and respect for you. Thank you for making me humble and wiser. 
Slowly and Steadily.


Listen on Spotify-

https://open.spotify.com/track/7yeA5sz8pPBkEaUnH7WuCR?si=bVJN7XnIQHKiM3Sj6r6fMA

Listen on Apple Music-

https://music.apple.com/np/album/timi-merai-single/1857765272

Available on Instagram, Tiktok and Facebook.

To all the lovers who're struggling with life's unknown forces, I wish this song brings you closer to each other.

#timrolagi

This time, I dedicate this song to the one who picks me up every single time I fall. I may not be good with my words but that won't change my love and respect for you. Thank you for making me humble and wiser. 
Slowly and Steadily.


Listen on Spotify-

https://open.spotify.com/track/7yeA5sz8pPBkEaUnH7WuCR?si=bVJN7XnIQHKiM3Sj6r6fMA

Listen on Apple Music-

https://music.apple.com/np/album/timi-merai-single/1857765272

Available on Instagram, Tiktok and Facebook.

To all the lovers who're struggling with life's unknown forces, I wish this song brings you closer to each other.

#timrolagi

snippet.title: Twin Strings Lounge - Sufiyana Sham 2 | SE 2 ‚Ä¢ EP 1
snippet.description:
After receiving overwhelming love on Sufiyana Shaam 1, we knew we had to bring this feeling back but deeper and more heartfelt. Presenting Sufiyana Shaam 2 a continuation of a moment that started with you all. This time, we wanted to create something that you can play on quiet evenings, long drives, or those nights when music speaks louder than words.

For Band Booking & Business Queries | Artkonnect +91 9643654363

‚Ä¢ A Twin Strings Production ‚Ä¢

Vocals/E Guitar: Manav
Acoustic Guitar: Sagar
Keyboard: Sahil
Zendrum: Mohit Deen

Directed and Edited by Twin Strings
Music by Twin Strings

Ft. Revati Khattar (weddingchoreographybyrevati)
 w/ Apoorva Singh & Arhana Jain

Special thanks to Arjun Lounge for the amazing clothes. (https://www.instagram.com/arjunloungestudio?igsh=cjk4aGFoeDNxeXpo) 

Audio Credits:
Additional Vocals: Ritik Bhardwaj, Isha Chakravorty
Drums: Vijay Kumar
Bass: Langmuansiam Naulak
Supporting Vocals : Aryan Bir
Tabla: Rohit Chawla
Dholak: Danish Sharma
Flute: Gautam Dayal
Violin & Cello: Sayan Sinha & Aliaksandra Bandarchuk (Gooseberry Ensemble)
Recorded, Produced, Mixed Mastered at TS Studio.

Video Team Credits:
A Twin Strings Production (in association w/ Shadow Craft Films)

DOP: Nitin Goyal Cam
Edit: Twin Strings
Edit Organise & Graphics : Nikunj Agrawal
Cinematographer: Imran Ansari
Associate Cinematographer: Vikas
Colorist: Imran Ansari
BTS: Krish
Production Controller: Azam Qureshi
Makeup: Jayanti
Gaffer: Satya
Decor & Execution: Noor Sahar
Styling : Muskan

#TwinStringsLounge #Sufiyanasham
